    <div class="col-sm-6 d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="paragraph">
            Structure

            The Mothershipâ€™s structural system looks to the future, and conforms to an efficient, rigid, mirrored grid. It implements a system similar to the Bone Steel Structure System developed in California.

            <br /><br />
            Members have â€˜smart highwaysâ€™ - pre-cut openings in various elements of the structure are ready to accommodate electricity, ventilation and heating. these highways provide easy routing while simplifying installation work and maintenance.
        </div>

